{
  "stem": "25639.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were concerned, according to some of these articles, that we will bring in these dreadful diseases for which they have no cure, and suppose it spreads to the population.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How will they deal with it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were very real problems and I couldn't blame them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were totally strangers and it's true, Sweden was not involved in the war, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not directly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the German army had to go through Sweden to go to-- get to Norway, but they had to promise that they let them through, otherwise Sweden had-- would have been taken, as well.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time that I was in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, while I was in quarantine, after a few days, I began to go out-- outside to the yard-- there was a big yard-- and I saw lots of bicycles parked there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked the doctor if I could use a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the nurses and the doctors come by bicycle, and I should pick any I want, and I could ride around the school yard.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How wonderful, I said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a bicycle in Czechoslovakia, and-- and I inherited my-- Victor's bicycle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, I'd like to say something about Victor later, which I-- and about the entire family-- who survived and where they went and how they were rescued, before-- please remind me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so there I was, riding around the schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 15 at this time, and this is how I met the Swedish family who came to visit me regularly after that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They inquired about me through the doctor, the Swedish doctor, as to what shape am I in?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
